{%- comment -%} Memorial Day Sale — Ian variant. Same body as control, hero swapped to Ian portrait + product square split. 35% off sitewide. Ends 2026-05-26 23:59 ET. v1 {%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign discount_pct = section.settings.discount_pct | default: 35
  assign keep_pct = 100 | minus: discount_pct
  assign end_iso = section.settings.end_iso | default: '2026-05-26T23:59:59-04:00'

  comment
    Spotlight handles — best sellers tied to specific benefit hooks.
    WLP-1, Berberine, Magnesium Glycinate, Vitamin D+K. Keep total under the 20-product all_products cap.
  endcomment
  assign spotlight_handles = 'wlp-1,berberine,magnesium-glycinate,vitamin-d-k' | split: ','

  comment
    Goal buckets for the bubble filter on the shop-all grid.
  endcomment
  assign goal_longevity = 'the-best-sellers-stack,longevity,coq10,energy,curcumin,daily-basics,starter-pack,spring-essentials-stack,vitamin-d-k' | split: ','
  assign goal_metab = 'berberine,hormone-metabolism,wlp-1,weight-management-stack,glp-1-nutrient-support-stack,metabolic-balance-stack' | split: ','
  assign goal_sleep = 'sleep,calm,magnesium-glycinate,advanced-sleep-recovery-set,magnesium-sleep-bundle,magnesium-calm-bundle,rest-recovery-stack,calm-energy-bundle,best-sellers-bundle' | split: ','
  assign goal_immunity = 'restore,curcumin,inflammation-immunity,vitamin-d-k,magnesium-restore-bundle' | split: ','

  comment
    Iteration source for the shop-all grid. Editor populates section.settings.sale_products (bypasses 20-product cap).
    Fallback to a curated handle list if editor hasn't populated.
  endcomment
  assign products_list = section.settings.sale_products
  assign display_handles = 'wlp-1,berberine,magnesium-glycinate,daily-basics,weight-management-stack,hormone-metabolism,restore,sleep,calm,coq10,vitamin-d-k,advanced-sleep-recovery-set,curcumin,the-best-sellers-stack,starter-pack,longevity,inflammation-immunity,energy,glp-1-nutrient-support-stack,metabolic-balance-stack' | split: ','

  assign meta_handles = 'wlp-1,berberine,magnesium-glycinate,daily-basics,weight-management-stack,hormone-metabolism,restore,best-sellers-bundle,metabolic-balance-stack,sleep,calm,coq10,vitamin-d-k,advanced-sleep-recovery-set,curcumin,the-best-sellers-stack,starter-pack,longevity,inflammation-immunity,energy,glp-1-nutrient-support-stack,magnesium-sleep-bundle,magnesium-calm-bundle,rest-recovery-stack,magnesium-restore-bundle' | split: ','
  assign pills = 'Weight Management|Hydrate & Detox|Restorative Sleep|Daily Foundations|Weight Management|Metabolism & Hormones|Hydrate & Recovery|Bestseller Bundle|Metabolic Stack|Restorative Sleep|Manage Stress|Energy & Recovery|Immunity & Mood|Sleep + Recovery|Immunity & Antioxidant|Bestseller|Daily Foundations|Longevity|Immunity & Inflammation|Energy & Focus|GLP-1 Support|Sleep & Magnesium|Calm & Magnesium|Rest + Recovery|Hydrate & Recover' | split: '|'
  assign badges = 'Top Seller|Top Seller|Top Seller|||||Best Value|||||||||||||||||' | split: '|'
  assign ratings = '4.78|4.84|4.97|4.83|4.85|4.85|4.94|4.92|4.85|4.88|4.94|4.82|4.87|4.91|4.81|4.92|4.89|4.83|4.87|4.86|4.84|4.87|4.88|4.90|4.89' | split: '|'
  assign reviews = '154|85|368|88|121|121|246|184|94|246|300|64|142|96|71|412|109|88|142|192|58|62|66|82|74' | split: '|'

  comment
    Tile image overrides where the featured image isn't the right tile shot.
  endcomment
  assign override_handles = 'restore,sleep,calm,energy,magnesium-sleep-bundle' | split: ','
  assign override_urls = 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Restore-Bag_af4e1a3f-f6ca-4ab7-bebf-7e492e6dac9b.png?v=1768255861&width=960|https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Sleep-Bag_9a994c43-7d98-40a8-ab98-2f20070e69d3.png?v=1768256290&width=960|https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Calm-Bag_42e47801-bfd1-4ce0-8f26-de468bc3d559.png?v=1768256004&width=960|https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Energy_3de78348-83c6-475b-aa3f-9df089873398.png?v=1768256691&width=960|https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/sleep-bag-mag-bundle.png?v=1768005885&width=960' | split: '|'

  comment
    Spotlight pre-canned copy. Parallel arrays indexed by spotlight_handles.
  endcomment
  assign spot_hooks = 'Appetite + metabolic support|Blood sugar + lipid balance|Deep sleep + nervous system|Daily immune + bone foundation' | split: '|'
  assign spot_headlines = 'Curb the cravings. Burn smarter.|Stabilize blood sugar. The way your body wants.|The mineral 50% of us are short on.|The sunlight nutrient. Properly absorbed.' | split: '|'
  assign spot_bodies = 'WLP-1 supports the same GLP-1 pathways that govern appetite and metabolism, without a prescription. Our liposomal delivery means more of it actually reaches your bloodstream.|Berberine is the most-studied natural compound for blood sugar and lipid balance. Our extra-strength 1000mg formula absorbs 6.2x more than standard berberine.|Magnesium runs more than 300 reactions in your body. Most forms barely absorb. Our glycinate-chelated form delivers it where it goes to work for deep sleep, calm nerves, and recovered muscle.|Vitamin D is fat-soluble, but most pills are taken without fat. Our liposomal D+K2 delivers up to 149x more vitamin D into your bloodstream than the standard pill.' | split: '|'
  assign spot_subs = 'Curb cravings. Burn smarter.|Stabilize blood sugar, naturally.|The mineral most of us are short on.|The sunlight nutrient, properly absorbed.' | split: '|'
  assign spot_bullets = 'Curbs cravings without a prescription~Supports appetite + metabolism~Liposomal delivery for real absorption||1000mg extra-strength formula~6.2x more absorbable than standard~Supports blood sugar + lipid balance||Chelated for full absorption~Calms the nervous system~Deeper sleep, less morning grog||Liposomal D + K2 combo~Up to 149x more absorbable~Daily bone, immune + mood support' | split: '||'

  comment
    Matches theme setting `data__product__excluded_pdp_selling_plan_names` so lander shows the same
    curated cadences as the PDP. Pipe-delimited with leading/trailing pipes for `contains` checks.
  endcomment
  assign excluded_plan_names = '|Every 2 Week(s)|Every 1 Month(s)|Every 2 Month(s)|Every 3 Month(s)|Every 6 Month(s)|Every 3 months backend|Every 6 months backend|'
-%}

{%- comment -%} Build the modal product database. Iterates the same source as the grid so the 20-product
all_products cap doesn't truncate the JSON when the editor populates `sale_products`. {%- endcomment -%}
{%- if products_list != blank and products_list.size > 0 -%}
  {%- assign json_source = products_list -%}
  {%- assign json_is_objects = true -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- assign json_source = display_handles -%}
  {%- assign json_is_objects = false -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- capture products_json -%}
{
  {%- assign emitted_first = false -%}
  {%- for entry in json_source -%}
    {%- if json_is_objects -%}{%- assign p = entry -%}{%- else -%}{%- assign p = all_products[entry] -%}{%- endif -%}
    {%- if p != blank and p.handle != blank -%}
      {%- if emitted_first -%},{%- endif -%}{%- assign emitted_first = true -%}
      {%- assign smart_desc = p.metafields.smart.description | default: p.description | strip_html | truncate: 360 -%}
      {%- capture bullet_color -%}{{ p.metafields.custom.smart_bullet_point_color }}{%- endcapture -%}
      {%- if bullet_color == blank -%}{%- capture bullet_color -%}{{ p.metafields.custom.primary_color }}{%- endcapture -%}{%- endif -%}
      {%- if bullet_color == blank -%}{%- assign bullet_color = '#DB3519' -%}{%- endif -%}
      {%- assign main_img_src = p.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 -%}
      {%- case p.handle -%}
        {%- when 'restore' -%}{%- assign main_img_src = 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0821/3997/1873/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Restore-Bag_af4e1a3f-f6ca-4ab7-bebf-7e492e6dac9b.png?v=1768255861&width=800' -%}
        {%- when 'sleep' -%}{%- assign main_img_src = 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Sleep-Bag_9a994c43-7d98-40a8-ab98-2f20070e69d3.png?v=1768256290&width=800' -%}
        {%- when 'calm' -%}{%- assign main_img_src = 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0821/3997/1873/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Calm-Bag_42e47801-bfd1-4ce0-8f26-de468bc3d559.png?v=1768256004&width=800' -%}
        {%- when 'energy' -%}{%- assign main_img_src = 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Energy_3de78348-83c6-475b-aa3f-9df089873398.png?v=1768256691&width=800' -%}
        {%- when 'magnesium-sleep-bundle' -%}{%- assign main_img_src = 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/sleep-bag-mag-bundle.png?v=1768005885&width=800' -%}
      {%- endcase -%}
      "{{ p.handle }}": {
        "title": {{ p.title | json }},
        "handle": {{ p.handle | json }},
        "price": {{ p.price }},
        "compare_at_price": {{ p.compare_at_price | default: 0 }},
        "image": {{ main_img_src | json }},
        "images": [{%- for img in p.images limit: 8 -%}{{ img | image_url: width: 800 | json }}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- endfor -%}],
        "description": {{ smart_desc | json }},
        "bullets": [{%- for b in p.metafields.custom.smart_bullet_points.value -%}{{ b | json }}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- endfor -%}],
        "bullet_color": {{ bullet_color | json }},
        "options": [{%- for opt in p.options_with_values -%}{"name": {{ opt.name | json }}, "values": [{%- for v in opt.values -%}{{ v | json }}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- endfor -%}]}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- endfor -%}],
        "variants": [{%- for v in p.variants -%}{"id": {{ v.id }}, "title": {{ v.title | json }}, "price": {{ v.price }}, "option1": {{ v.option1 | json }}, "option2": {{ v.option2 | json }}, "option3": {{ v.option3 | json }}, "available": {{ v.available }}, "selling_plans": [
          {%- assign first_plan = true -%}
          {%- for spa in v.selling_plan_allocations -%}
            {%- assign plan_lookup = '|' | append: spa.selling_plan.name | append: '|' -%}
            {%- unless excluded_plan_names contains plan_lookup -%}
              {%- unless first_plan -%},{%- endunless -%}
              {"id": {{ spa.selling_plan.id }}, "name": {{ spa.selling_plan.name | json }}, "price": {{ spa.price }}}
              {%- assign first_plan = false -%}
            {%- endunless -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
        ]}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- endfor -%}]
      }
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
}
{%- endcapture -%}

<style>
  .lnd-md { font-family: inherit; color: #0D273E; --md-navy: #0D273E; --md-red: #DB3519; --md-navy-2: #143452; --md-cream: #efe9dd; --md-bg: #f6f6f4; --md-blue: #4659FF; }
  .lnd-md * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  /* Sticky promo bar with countdown (incl. seconds) */
  .lnd-md__bar { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50; background: var(--md-red); color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; gap: 10px 16px; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.2; }
  .lnd-md__bar-headline { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; }
  .lnd-md__bar-count { display: inline-flex; gap: 4px; align-items: center; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .lnd-md__bar-count > span:first-child { margin-right: 4px; font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.9; }
  .lnd-md__bar-count .chip { display: inline-flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 2px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.22); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22); border-radius: 6px; padding: 4px 6px; min-width: 34px; justify-content: center; }
  .lnd-md__bar-count .chip b { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
  .lnd-md__bar-count .chip span { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.85; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }

  /* HERO — Ian variant: solid navy bg, image card (Ian + product square) above text on mobile, side-by-side on desktop. */
  .lnd-md__hero { position: relative; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--md-navy) 0%, var(--md-navy-2) 100%); color: #fff; overflow: hidden; }
  .lnd-md__hero-inner { position: relative; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; padding: 22px 20px 30px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 22px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-media { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.55fr 1fr; gap: 10px; align-items: stretch; }
  .lnd-md__hero-ian { position: relative; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; background: #0b1f30; box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
  .lnd-md__hero-ian img { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 4/5; }
  .lnd-md__hero-ian-tag { position: absolute; left: 10px; bottom: 10px; right: 10px; background: rgba(13,39,62,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(6px); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.25; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
  .lnd-md__hero-ian-tag b { display: block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-product { position: relative; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--md-red); box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .lnd-md__hero-product img { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; aspect-ratio: 4/5; }
  .lnd-md__hero-product-tag { position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; background: #fff; color: var(--md-red); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 7px 12px; border-radius: 999px; box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .lnd-md__hero-text { text-align: left; max-width: 580px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-eyebrow { display: inline-block; background: var(--md-red); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 7px 12px; border-radius: 999px; margin: 0 0 14px; line-height: 1.2; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); }
  .lnd-md__hero h1 { font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.04; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .lnd-md__hero h1 em { color: var(--md-red); font-style: normal; }
  .lnd-md__hero p.lead { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.95; margin: 0 0 14px; max-width: 480px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .lnd-md__hero p.lead b { color: #fff; font-weight: 800; }
  .lnd-md__hero-rotator { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18); border-radius: 14px; padding: 10px 14px; margin: 0 0 14px; max-width: 440px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-rotator-line { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; gap: 6px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-rotator-line .static { opacity: 0.9; }
  .lnd-md__hero-rotator-line .dynamic { color: var(--md-red); font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; transition: opacity 0.35s ease, transform 0.35s ease; display: inline-block; min-width: 110px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-rotator-line .dynamic.is-out { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
  .lnd-md__hero-bullets { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 18px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; max-width: 480px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-bullets li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.35; }
  .lnd-md__hero-bullets li em { color: var(--md-red); font-style: normal; font-weight: 800; }
  .lnd-md__hero-bullets .check { flex-shrink: 0; width: 22px; height: 22px; background: var(--md-red); color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900; margin-top: 1px; }
  .lnd-md__hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--md-red); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .lnd-md__hero-fineprint { font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.7; margin: 10px 0 0; max-width: 460px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* Value strip */
  .lnd-md__values { background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid #eee; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 18px 16px; }
  .lnd-md__values-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 14px 18px; }
  .lnd-md__value { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--md-navy); line-height: 1.3; }
  .lnd-md__value svg { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--md-red); }

  /* Absorption brand band */
  .lnd-md__brand { background: var(--md-bg); padding: 40px 20px; }
  .lnd-md__brand-inner { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .lnd-md__brand-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--md-red); margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .lnd-md__brand h2 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.15; }
  .lnd-md__brand h2 em { color: var(--md-blue); font-style: normal; }
  .lnd-md__brand p { font-size: 15px; color: #444; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .lnd-md__reasons { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 18px 0 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .lnd-md__reasons li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ececec; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; }
  .lnd-md__reasons .num { flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--md-blue); color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
  .lnd-md__reasons li > div { font-size: 14px; color: #333; line-height: 1.5; }
  .lnd-md__reasons b { color: var(--md-navy); font-weight: 800; }
  .lnd-md__brand-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin: 22px 0 0; }
  .lnd-md__brand-stat { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ececec; border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px 14px; text-align: center; }
  .lnd-md__brand-stat b { display: block; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--md-blue); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 4px; }
  .lnd-md__brand-stat span { font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.35; display: block; }

  /* Testimonial band */
  .lnd-md__testimonial { background: var(--md-navy); color: #fff; padding: 44px 20px; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--md-red); margin: 0 0 12px; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-stars { color: #f5b800; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-quote { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0 0 18px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-author { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.75; margin: 0; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-dots { display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center; margin: 20px 0 0; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-dot.is-active { background: var(--md-red); }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-slide { display: none; min-height: 160px; }
  .lnd-md__testimonial-slide.is-active { display: block; }

  /* Spotlight cards */
  .lnd-md__spots { padding: 40px 16px; background: #fff; }
  .lnd-md__spots-head { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto 22px; text-align: center; }
  .lnd-md__spots-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--md-red); margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .lnd-md__spots-head h2 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .lnd-md__spots-pipe { color: var(--md-red); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 6px; opacity: 0.85; }
  .lnd-md__spots-head p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin: 0; }
  .lnd-md__spots-grid { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 14px; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile { position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ececec; border-radius: 16px; padding: 12px 12px 14px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease; overflow: hidden; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: var(--md-red); border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(13,39,62,0.1); border-color: var(--md-navy); }
  .lnd-md__spot-ribbon { position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; background: var(--md-navy); color: #fff; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 5px 9px; border-radius: 999px; text-transform: uppercase; z-index: 2; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile-img { aspect-ratio: 1/1; background: var(--md-cream); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 8px 0 12px; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; display: block; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 4px; color: var(--md-navy); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #6b6b6b; line-height: 1.35; margin: 0 0 10px; min-height: 32px; }
  .lnd-md__spot-tile-bullets { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
