    <div class="lnd-md__testimonial-inner">
      <div class="lnd-md__testimonial-eyebrow">Real Customers · Real Results</div>
      <div class="lnd-md__testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <div class="lnd-md__testimonial-slide is-active">
        <p class="lnd-md__testimonial-quote">"I've taken magnesium for years and never felt it. With theirs I sleep through the night within a week. The difference is absorption. Finally."</p>
        <p class="lnd-md__testimonial-author">Lauren M. · Verified Magnesium Glycinate buyer</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lnd-md__testimonial-slide">
        <p class="lnd-md__testimonial-quote">"Dropped ~9 lbs in two months on WLP-1 plus walks. No jitters, no crash. The cravings I used to fight at 3pm just stopped showing up."</p>
        <p class="lnd-md__testimonial-author">Marcus T. · Verified WLP-1 buyer</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lnd-md__testimonial-slide">
        <p class="lnd-md__testimonial-quote">"My A1C dropped a full point in 90 days. My doctor asked what changed. I told her the berberine actually absorbs."</p>
